title: Exclusive Episode: Answering YOUR Questions on Baby Huff
description:
Sadie and Christian are having a baby! On this weeks exclusive episode, The Huff’s dive into your questions about Baby Huff. Listen in as they discuss when and how they found out they were expecting, what they are most excited about, and of course, the best piece of parenting advice they have ever received. **Be sure to check out Sadie’s YouTube page for additional bonus footage of their pregnancy story! **
